\ CLST              >> clear the stack
\ 5 REG41 RCL FS.   >> 10.0 is in X
\ 5.0 CLRGX REG41   >> clear the reg 5 of REG41
\ 5 REG41 RCL FS.   >> 0.0 into the stack at X
\ --------------------------------------------------------------
